nomenon,</I> whereas the <I>Parallaxes</I> aba$e it. Now of what little
$tead this lamentable refuge is, judge by this, that in ca$e that effectof
the refractions were of $uch an efficacy, as that which not long time
$ince $ome A$tronomers have introduced, the mo$t that they could
