<marg>* Shelter.</marg>
fort of Man, and ^{*} Covert of Bea$ts. The fourth part begins
at <I>Ver$e</I> 20. celebrating the fourth dayes work, <I>viz.</I> The Sun
and Moon, but chiefly the commodiou$ne$$e of tho$e things,
which in their Sea$ons befall to all Living Creatures and to Man;
