Earths rotundity; Sacred was <I>Augu$tine,</I> who granted the Earth
to be round, but denyed the <I>Antipodes</I>; Sacred is the ^{*}Liturgy of
<marg>* Officium</marg>
our Moderns, who admit the $mallne$$e of the Earth, but deny
