<P>In obedience to the command of the No-
ble <I>Signore Vincenzo Carraffa,</I> a Neapo-
litan, and Knight of S. <I>John of Jeru-
$alem,</I> (a per$on, to $peak the truth, of
$o great Merit, that in him Nobility of
