of its Light? And if that Fire and this Light $hould reunite toge-
ther, which yet is no impo$$ibility, in regard, that at the fir$t
they lay in that little room, what a Conden$ation would this be?
If you $tudy for them, you will find hundreds of $uch Rarefacti-
