$ame manner $ee the odoriferous Atomes concurre to the con$titu-
tion of the Oderate Solids; but where Sen$ible Ob$ervation is
wanting, we are to $upply it with Rea$on, which will $uffice to
make us apprehen$ive, no le$$e of the Motion to the Rarefaction
and re$olution of Solids, than, to the Conden$ation of rare and
mo$t tenuous Sub$tances. Moreover, we que$tion how to effect
the Conden$ation and Rarefaction of the Bodies which may be
rarefied and conden$ed, $tudying in what manner it may be done
