<P>SIMP. <I>Ari$totle,</I> as neer as I can remember, breaks out again$t
certain of the Ancients, who introduced Vacuity, as nece$$ary
to Motion, $aying, that this without that could not be effected;
<foot>to</foot>
<p n=>51</p>
to this <I>Ari$totle</I> making oppo$ition, demon$trateth, that on the
