ther heavy matter on three $trings of different lengths, but in
$uch proportion, that while the longer maketh two Vibrations,
<foot>the</foot>
<p n=>88</p>
the $horter may make four, and the middle one three; which
will happen, when the longe$t containeth $ixteen feet, or other
mea$ures, of which the middle one containeth nine, and the
$horte$t four: and removing them all together from Perpendi-
