<p n=>111</p>
were $et, not in the mid$t, but neerer to one of the ends.</P>
<P>SAGR. I think the Problem is toucht upon by <I>Ari$totle</I> in his
<I>Mechanical Que$tions.</I></P>
<P>SALV. The Que$tion of <I>Aristotle</I> is not preci$ely the $ame,
