Line upon the Plane of the Pri$me.</P>
<P>SALV. There are $everal waies to draw tho$e Lines, but two
<marg><I>Several waies to
de$cribe a Para-
bola.</I></marg>
that are more expedite than all the re$t, I will de$cribe unto you.
