ven one, and taken in any part of the $aid Per-
pendicular, $hall be afterwards pa$t by the
$ame Moveable.</P>
<P><I>In the Perpendicular A B let A C be any Space taken from the be-
ginning of the Motion in A, to which let D B be another equal Space
