<head>PROBL X. PROP. XXVI.</head>
<P>A Perpendicular between two Horizontal <I>P</I>aral-
lel Lines, as al$o a Space greater than the $aid
<I>P</I>erpendicular, but le$$e than double the $ame,
being given, to rai$e a <I>P</I>lane between the $aid
<I>P</I>arallels from the lowe$t Term of the <I>P</I>er-
pendicular, along which the Moveable may
with a Reflex Motion after the Fall along the
<I>P</I>erpendicular pa$$e a Space equal to the Space
