Fall along the <I>P</I>erpendicular.</P>
<foot><I>Let</I></foot>
<p n=>185</p>
<P><I>Let A B be a Perpendicular between the Horizontal Parallels A O
and B C; and let F E be greater than B A, but le$$e than double
the $ame. It is required between the $aid Parallels from the point
B to rai$e a Plane, along which the Moveable after the Fall from A to
