gure prefixed; wherein the Leaver
is repre$ented by the Bar of wood
or other $olid matter, <I>B</I> C D, let
<fig>
the heavy Weight to be rai$ed be
A, and let the $teadfa$t $upport
or Fulciment on which the Leaver
