ding to the proportion by which the Perpendicular C H is le$s than
A C: and that along the Plane A D, the Force hath the $ame pro-
portion to the Weight, that the Perpendicular I D hath to D A:
and, la$tly, that in the Plane A E the <I>F</I>orce to the Weight ob$er-
veth the proportion of E K and E A.</P>
