<head>PROP. VII. THE OR. VII.</head>
<P><I>The Right Portion of a Rightangled Conoid lighter
than the Liquid, when it $hall have its Axis greater
than Se$quialter of the Semi-parameter, but le$$e
than to be unto the $aid Semi-parameter in proportion
