as that its Ba$e be wholly within the Liquid, it $hall
never $tand $o as that its Ba$e do touch the Surface
of the Liquid, but $o, that it be wholly within the
Liquid, and $hall not in the lea$t touch its Surface.</I></P>
<P>Let there be a Portion as hath been $aid; and let it be de-
