as are the Guns, the Shot, and any kind of Balla$t, which is pre$up-
po$ed to be in the Hold, and of other things of impediment; and
when the$e Ships are thus cleared, you mu$t $top all the Loop-holes,
Cat-holes, Skuppers and Hau$es, which you $hall finde between or
