And next you mu$t join or grapple the$e two Ships together with five
or more Tires or Orders of thick and $trong Beames tripplicated;
that is, that each of the $aid Orders con$i$t of three Beams, joyned
lengthways; and that each of the three Beams be $omewhat longer
than the bredth of the Deck or Hull of each Ship; and that theybe
