are to proceed till you have taken all the water from the one &amp; the
other of the two Ships: In $o doing, you $hall $ee the two Shpis lea-
$urely and gently rai$e the Ship that was $unk, $o high above the
Surface of the water, that you may commodiou$ly free it, and
