Ship when it is found, as well in deep as $hallow Channels, which
particulars I $hall re$erve for another time.</P>
<P>I will not $tand to $hew how this kind of Diving Machine might
be made of Boards, and that in $undry fa$hions, well calked and
pitcht, with four Lights or Sights, fa$tening about the mouth of the
$ame as much Lead as $hould be nece$$ary, ora$inuch as by what
hath been $poken in the third Explanation, it is $ufficiently manife$t.
